column3: Some bad bugs are around hereâ€¦
The garbs of the gients hang over me.
My usual grounds only bared by towering planks of wood
The tools of the giants rusted and old.
Traversing the stairs has led you to higher grounds with more rooms.
There are many toys and other trinkets in this area.
The little giant sleeps in this area.
Mountains of clothes block my view of what is ahead.
A clean area with little trinkets to take
The area of which the giants and ants eat.
Pencils pens books and paper balls lie dormant in this knowledgable filled room
